title: Iron and Wine Bonnaroo 2005 MP3 mastered
description:
The famed, wonderful Bonnaroo performance by Iron & Wine edited to fit on one cd.

I went in and edited out a few minutes of crowd noise to fit the entire show on one 80 minute cd, though not leaving out much of Sam Beam&#039;s between-song chatter.  It&#039;s smoothed out so the tracks are seamless, and I also half-ass mastered it a little better to bring out the goodness.

Enjoy and seed this bastard, there are some great songs all in one set here!

-emptykay
